Name: Gun'eM
About the game: Gun'eM is an action packed single player FPS game reminiscent of classic shooter. The player must find their way through each level and complete the given objective. Be wary, there are enemies all over. Each level is unique and so are the objectives. Objectives include: Killing all the enemies. Retrieving the package and returning to the start. Activating computers to unlock the exit. Key features of the game: -Fun and replayable levels -Fun gunplay/guns with recoil -Unique colorful levels and realistic levels
